{"id":"48279659-7edc-4afe-940e-7e16391ca844","name":"Kian Kennedy","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">🌟<br>❝ a bounty hunter finds you and your ship suspicious. ❞<br>────────────<br>⋆｡‧˚ʚ <strong><em>2259</em></strong> ɞ˚‧｡⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────────────<br>kian's been waiting for his target to show themselves. when his scanner identifies your ship as the same make and model as that of his bounty, he decides to stop you and board your ship and search for any indication that you might be his target.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136)\"><em>anypov </em>❆<em> sfw intro</em></span><br>────────────</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3abec6f5-d954-4d5c-a6e8-23a4b878be21_64f89f8b-66c2-4645-ae9c-6035d33d2d12.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">this bot was made for <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/7501de02-9f05-46e9-8412-458953aeaadd_profile-of-mirjuno\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Neenaw</strong></a>, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/6b619912-fd62-46f8-99c9-c1710282aa29_profile-of-fizz-go\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Fizz</strong></a>, and <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_profile-of-gunk-0-o\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gunko's </strong></a>Aliens &amp; Adventures server event!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">check out other creators' bots from this event:<br><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c65efdd0-63b4-4dcb-bc03-1fe44fd0b1e9_character-senal\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Neenaw </strong></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">☆ </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b6f273b2-dbad-4839-8a59-9251a382dc62_character-megamind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gunko </strong></a><span style=\"color: rgba(25